{"tid":932814,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone發微博撐中興華為捱批　環時總編嘆「被迫」用蘋果　因難適應華為系統","createTime":"2018-12-08T05:09:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-08T16:30:29.000Z","uid":178875,"like":97,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"117f7cc088cfa4c927a81fc1ae6e78a156180f47","tid":932814,"uid":178875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T05:09:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wQoSn53.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwQoSn53.jpg&h=1550ee35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美澳紐早前以國家安全為由，禁止5G網絡使用中國電訊巨華為的設備，日本昨傳出將禁止政府採購華為及中興通訊電訊設備。內地《環球時報》總編輯胡錫進今在北京舉行的該報年會開幕禮上致辭，回應了內地網民批評他在美國「封殺」中興時仍使用iPhone一事，表示自己曾嘗試放棄iPhone、試用華為手機，但發現不能適應其操作系統，於是「被迫堅持用iPhone」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2PqVE2K\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2PqVE2K&d=2I7XgINVBACv%2BmOn8Yj1Iv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=f9715cd3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2PqVE2K</a>"},{"pid":"6614c9a478f6d680ffe83e4c11ad0e4fc14d4d4c","tid":932814,"uid":13257,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T05:13:11.000Z","msg":"即係唔好用囉"},{"pid":"5414ad08f214f2f9b06630cc13ab2af315a59e65","tid":932814,"uid":29080,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T05:13:43.000Z","msg":"渣ga <br />\n抑鬱上吊死啦"},{"pid":"b4591074d2195a79f1436bce8d619059db02bc2d","tid":932814,"uid":56999,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T05:16:47.000Z","msg":"ok<br />\n幾時被迫移民美國"},{"pid":"4e5dd202060ec18860cfc6d524ce4243bbe9b61e","tid":932814,"uid":25612,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T05:17:01.000Z","msg":"講到咁反美但係少少辛苦都適應唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeaa824397dc02193859d08f62e3041acc50fca7","tid":932814,"uid":77196,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T05:18:03.000Z","msg":"咁咪用小米囉，都跟住抄<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hk